    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The exterior maintains a strong shine, though you will find some minor surface scratches and a few small stone chips on the front bumper from normal highway driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only slight bolster wear on the driver's seat and minor scuffing on the door sills. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a consistent service history and all major systems functioning as intended. It represents a reliable option for someone looking for a solid, road-ready vehicle that shows only light signs of use.",
