    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for precise throttle response. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the integrity of the multi-link rear suspension under load. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh. It sits on staggered Style 67 alloys, maintaining the original suspension geometry for exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. A mechanically sorted example of a modern classic.",
